This repo contains the SELinux policy configuration of Third-Party vendor's features
(such as Microtrust teei) for all projects.
It is built in all projectes since MTK_WITHOUT_THIRD_PARTY_SEPOLICY isn't defined with yes by default.

Configuration files:
../../common/BoardConfig.mk
../../system/common/BoardConfig.mk
../../vendor/common/BoardConfig.mk
../../vendor/common/BoardConfig-vext.mk

Directory structure description:
./vendor:
These directories contains the MTK SELinux policy configuration for vendor.
It defines the domains and types for MTK services running in /vendor all devices.
It is built into vendor.img:/vendor/etc/selinux.

./private:
These directories contains the MTK SELinux policy configuration for platform private.
It extends the domains and types for the AOSP services and apps common to all devices.
It is built into system.img:/system/system_ext/etc/selinux or system_ext.img:
/system_ext/etc/selinux.

./public:
These directories contains the MTK SELinux policy configuration for platform public.
It defines the domains and types for MTK services running in /system all devices.
It is built into vendor.img:/vendor/etc/selinux & system.img:/system/system_ext/etc/selinux
or system_ext.img:/system_ext/etc/selinux.
